<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_188" id="94r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_188_r1l11"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Ludweıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Graf<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Ötıng<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l12">Hawbtman Jn <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan> payern etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_188_r1l13"><expan>Wolgeborn<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der kleynöt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l14"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe dıe hochgeborn <expan>fürſtin<ex>en</ex></expan> . fraw Elıſabeth von Cleue . <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒogin</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l15">in payern wıtıb . <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex></expan> den Juden bey vns hab ſteen . etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l16">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır von der <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawn von payern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l18"><expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd bett <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıe Juden bey vns dıe dıe ſache antrıft . 
<add><ab facs="#facs_188_r1l17">vormals </ab></add> <expan>erbette<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l21">gehabt daʒ ſıe frıſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_188_r1l19">darumb </ab></add> haben <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bıs auf 
<add><ab facs="#facs_188_r1l20">ſand <expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> tag ʒu </ab></add> ſunwenten ſchıerıſt alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l22">daʒ ſıe vmb kein frıſt mer gebetten wurden . VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l23">wır <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden für vns beſant / vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu eren <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l24">mıt Jn gerett / daʒ ſıe vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſıe <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe <expan>vorge<ex>nante</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l25">kleynöt . noch ʒwen monat nach <expan>ſunwent<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan> <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l26">wıe wol Jn das gar vnfüklıch ſey . alſo daʒ ſıe fürbas vmb kein frıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l27">mer <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr gnade mıt fleıſſ Jr wellet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l28">daran ſein daʒ dıe Juden in der ʒeıt auſgerıcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . denn wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l29">wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_188" id="94r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludweig<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Öting<ex>en,</ex></expan> hawbtman in
                            <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Payern etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Wolgeborn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr gnade
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der kleynöt
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die die hochgeborn
                                <expan>fürstin<ex>en</ex></expan> fraw Elisabeth von Cleve,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogin</expan> in Payern, witib,
                                <expan>und<ex>er</ex></expan> den juden bey uns hab steen etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        von der <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawn von Payern
                            <expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und bett <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        die juden bey uns, die die sache antrift, <add>vormals</add>
<expan>erbette<ex>n</ex></expan> gehabt, daz sie frist <add>darumb</add>
                        haben <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bis auf <app><note><q type="date"><add>sand
                            <expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> tag zu</add> sunwenten schierist</q>24.06.1415</note></app>,
                        also daz sie umb kein frist mer gebetten wurden. Wie
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden für uns besant und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit
                        in gerett, daz sie uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, sie <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die
                                <expan>vorge<ex>nante</ex>n</expan> kleynöt noch zwen monat nach
                                <expan>sunwent<ex>en</ex></expan> schierist
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan>
<expan>halte<ex>n,</ex></expan> wie wol in das gar unfüklich sey, also daz
                        sie fürbas umb kein frist mer <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr gnade
                        mit fleiss, ir wellet daran sein, daz die juden in der zeit ausgericht
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
